{"tid":1856873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明報：市民網購口罩運港，但郵政署因卜木竹一大肺炎只提供有限度服務","createTime":"2020-02-02T00:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T02:43:23.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5ba1d502168d067ae84ab63775b199ccd2ad50","tid":1856873,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:45:00.000Z","msg":"不少市民近日選擇網購口罩運港，但郵政署因卜木竹一大肺炎只提供有限度服務。有郵政署工會指出，估計目前最少有1.8萬件包裹堆積在空郵中心，部分為口罩，但只有一半人手工作。郵政署回應說，現時約有3000件載有口罩的郵件候派，會以「口罩先派」原則，會在周一（3日）完成派遞。<br />\n<br />\n#明報 #明報即時新聞 #香港郵政 #郵政署 #工會 #空郵中心 #包裹 #口罩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/498203090239831/posts/2840777239315726/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F498203090239831%2Fposts%2F2840777239315726%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=2eb1b195\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/498203090239831/posts/2840777239315726/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"277a35a719f9221a86e5d9fb90c43148c5f0f7bb","tid":1856873,"uid":24339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c361eb514c0d5759399e39c48e08e6101e894d","tid":1856873,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:46:29.000Z","msg":"信報無信，明報不明，蘋果爛咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab4158d007928a080cfc1f57cff69408130b093","tid":1856873,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35fe24e9cf3714e8dd1b5a61c1f266edda27612","tid":1856873,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T01:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKmdFP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c